Every month, 2.5 million data are included, and customers receive updates every two days.
The elaboration of this huge flow of information allows these companies to give them different uses and offer a variety of products.
The most frequent use focuses on repair and maintenance, but depending on which countries there are also tools for scrapping parts management or for calculating the venal or residual value of a car.
